headline: Trolled, Taiwan Sees China’s Meddling
abstract: The self-governing island is on high alert for digital-age trickery and deception that Beijing might be using to try to swing a crucial election.
lead_paragraph: TAIPEI, Taiwan — At first glance, the bespectacled YouTuber railing against Taiwan’s president, Tsai Ing-wen, just seems like a concerned citizen making an appeal to his fellow Taiwanese.
